 Supergrass 宣布“I Should Coco” 30 周年纪念巡演https://www.nme.com/news/music/supergrass-announce-i-should-coco-30th-anniversary-tour-tickets-2025-3794055?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=supergrass-announce-i-should-可可-30 周年-巡演-门票-2025Adam England Mon, 16 Sep 2024 07:54:42 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieLive Music News https://www.nme.com/?p=3794055 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Supergrass-Live-Tour.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="超级草" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Supergrass-Live-Tour.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Supergrass-Live-Tour-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Supergrass-Live-Tour-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Supergrass-Live-Tour-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Supergrass-Live-Tour-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Supergrass-Live-Tour-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “不包括动态定价”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/supergrass-announce-i-should-coco-30th-anniversary-tour-tickets-2025-3794055">Supergrass 宣布“I Should Coco” 30 周年纪念巡演的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Supergrass-Live-Tour.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="超级草" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Supergrass-Live-Tour.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Supergrass-Live-Tour-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Supergrass-Live-Tour-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Supergrass-Live-Tour-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Supergrass-Live-Tour-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Supergrass-Live-Tour-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/supergrass">Supergrass</a>携 30 周年纪念巡演回归，庆祝“I Should Coco”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/gaz-coombes-interview-supergrass-reunion-billie-eilish-3367390">Gaz Coombes：“我觉得我正在写我写过的最好的东西”</a></strong></li></ul><p>乐队今天早上（9 月 16 日）宣布，他们将于 2025 年 5 月在格拉斯哥、诺丁汉、谢菲尔德、纽卡斯尔、伯明翰、卡迪夫和利兹举行一系列演出，庆祝首张专辑发行 30 周年。在伦敦 Roundhouse 举办的演出。</p><p>他们将完整演奏《I Should Coco》，然后再演一些他们最热门的歌曲。贝斯手 Mick Quinn 表示：“2025 年 5 月 15 日是《I Should Coco》问世 30 周年。 Supergrass 很高兴地宣布他们将回归并首次现场完整表演首张专辑。不包括动态定价。”</p><p> 《I Should Coco》于 1995 年 5 月 15 日发行，并首次在排行榜上排名第三。那年夏天晚些时候，Supergrass 在格拉斯顿伯里 (Glastonbury) 的演出之后，它登上了排行榜第一的位置，并在英国售出了超过 500,000 张。该专辑在全球销量超过 100 万张，是 Parlophone Records 自披头士乐队以来销量最高的首张专辑。</p><p>专辑中的曲目包括“Caught By The Fuzz”和“Alright”，后者在排行榜上排名第二。</p><p>查看下面的完整巡演日期，并<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fsupergrass-tickets%2Fartist%2F773872" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>查找门票。周三（9月18日）上午10点开始预售，周五（9月20日）上午9点开始正式发售。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_-FOaENKIf/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; heig