况下进行的。 </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bts-jungkook-shares-support-newjeans-ador-hybe-feud-3794005"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>在直播现已删除之前，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newjeans-voice-support-min-hee-jin-awards-ceremony-3791825">NewJeans 在本月早些时候的 The Fact Music Awards 颁奖典礼上发表获奖感言时表达了对 Min 的支持</a>。此前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newjeans-hanni-minji-danielle-voice-frustration-ador-hybe-feud-3789993">女团三名成员在网上发帖表达了对ADOR和HYBE之间持续不和的不满</a>。</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ex-ador-ceo-min-hee-jin-files-injunction-to-be-reappointed-as-internal-director-3794019">前 ADOR 首席执行官 Min Hee-jin 提交了重新任命为内部董事的禁令，该禁令</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
